<normalizedToken id="E9A7B733809F56993391FC429D5624CC" originalValue="Jäger">Jaeger</normalizedToken>
, 2008. 4-6 Left male palp (4 prolateral 5 ventral 6 retrolateral) 7 epigyne, ventral 8 vulva, dorsal. Abbreviations: 
<normalizedToken id="052AEE4AB13430E111DB7BA6A0CC8FE3" originalValue="AB–anterior">AB-anterior</normalizedToken>
