structures of internal duct system, 
<normalizedToken id="8F69643E2D19B4DB9F4AE0B1957EC03B" originalValue="LW–lateral">LW-lateral</normalizedToken>
winding of internal duct system, 
<normalizedToken id="65A12DEE6E094A4905AD81BD40D89FC0" originalValue="PP–posterior">PP-posterior</normalizedToken>
