<normalizedToken id="457E525440B1AC582971CEE37CABAD87" originalValue="I–IV">I-IV</normalizedToken>
(male, right). Scale bars: 1 mm (9, 10, 16, 17); 0.2 mm (11-15); 2 mm (18-21).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="2A49F9F8DC7327280F50A1002B66288E" pageId="5" pageNumber="158">
