Female. For details see 
<bibRefCitation id="7B1BA8EC711A09C81DCAFF8108E1B7F4" author="Jaeger, P" journalOrPublisher="Arthropoda Selecta" pageId="5" pageNumber="158" pagination="105 - 110" title="Barylestis Simon, 1910 - first record in Asia with comments on its zoogeography (Araneae: Sparassidae: Heteropodinae)." volume="17" year="2008">
<normalizedToken id="81433D278A7B28327FE5C695530F7B42" originalValue="Jäger">Jaeger</normalizedToken>
(2008)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
